org.sd.crawl
Class ProcessorResult

java.lang.Object
  org.sd.crawl.ProcessorResult
All Implemented Interfaces:
Publishable
Direct Known Subclasses:
NGramProcessor.NGramResult, OrderedSetProcessorResult, SnippetProcessorResult
public abstract class ProcessorResult
extends java.lang.Object
implements Publishable

A container for the results of a page processor.

This container provides access to a String representation for its value, but the value need not (and usually should not) be represented as a string in the underlying implementation.

Author:
Spence Koehler
